---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="The career arc from ecologist to AI consultant — via government, startups, and Valencia.">
  <section>
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p class="lead mt-3">I&rsquo;ve spent the last decade building AI systems and leading teams in government, not-for-profits, and startups. I co-founded MantisNLP, an NLP consultancy, served as CTO for five years, and now work independently with organisations who need senior AI capability without the overhead of a full-time hire.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h2>The career arc</h2>
      <ol class="timeline">
        <li>
          <span class="timeline-role">Analyst</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">Cabinet Office</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="timeline-role">Senior Data Scientist</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">Department for Education &mdash; pioneered Reproducible Analytical Pipelines</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="timeline-role">Senior Data Scientist</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">GDS (Government Digital Service)</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="timeline-role">Volunteer Data Scientist</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">DataKind UK</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="timeline-role">Co-founder &amp; CTO</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">MantisNLP &mdash; built to profitability over 5 years</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="timeline-role">Associate</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">Public Digital &mdash; AI strategy for governments</span>
        </li>
        <li class="timeline-now">
          <span class="timeline-role">Independent AI Consultant</span>
          <span class="timeline-org">Based in Valencia, Spain</span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h2>The human stuff</h2>
      <p>I live in Valencia, Spain with my family. When I&rsquo;m not working, I&rsquo;m usually training for a triathlon, running along the Turia, or trying to improve my Spanish. My career path was unusual &mdash; I started as an ecologist, retrained in data science, and found my way to AI via government. That non-linear route means I bring a different perspective to most AI consultants: I understand research rigour, public interest constraints, and the gap between academic AI and production systems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h2>Speaking</h2>
      <p>I speak at conferences about AI leadership, responsible AI, and what actually works when deploying AI in government and mission-driven organisations.</p>
      <div class="card mt-3">
        <h3>All the mistakes I made as a first-time tech lead</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">PyData &middot; Leadership track</p>
        <p>An honest talk about the transition from individual contributor to tech leader &mdash; the mistakes, the lessons, and what I&rsquo;d do differently.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h2>More</h2>
      <div class="more-links">
        <a href="/archive" class="card-link">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Blog archive</h3>
            <p class="text-muted">Everything I&rsquo;ve written since 2014 &mdash; across Medium, Substack, government blogs, and machinegurning.blog.</p>
            <span class="read-more">View archive &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/papers" class="card-link">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Academic papers</h3>
            <p class="text-muted">Publications in data science, agroforestry, and soil carbon from my previous life as an ecologist.</p>
            <span class="read-more">View papers &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline li {
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.35rem;
    top: 0.35rem;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .timeline-now::before {
    background: var(--color-accent) !important;
  }

  .timeline-role {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline-org {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .more-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .more-links {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .read-more {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
